    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm001-cut01.m4a",
      "text": "新人マネージャーの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the new manager!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm001-cut02.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　誰もいない？\n……あれ？\n早く来過ぎちゃったかな～……？\nはっ！！　これは！？\n綺麗、みんな可愛い……！！\nやばい～～\nこっちも……みんな可愛い～\nわぁ～～！！\n尊い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Nobody’s here?\n…Huh?\nDid I get here too early?\nAh! What’s this?!\nBeautiful! Everyone’s so adorable!\nOh my~!\nOver here‚ too! Everyone’s so cuuute!\nWowww!\nSo precious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh001-cut01.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hashimoto-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm001-cut03.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ！\n新人マネージャーの橋本さとみでっす！\nよろしくお願いします、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agh!\nI’m the new manager‚ Satomi Hashimoto!\nNice to meet you‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 61.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。よろしく、橋本さん\n今日は出勤初日だし、力まないで大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you too‚Hashimoto-san.\nIt’s your first day at work‚ so it’s okay to take it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　まずは所属アイドルとの顔合わせと\n今後のスケジュール確認、ですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ sir! First‚ I’m going to meet and greet the idols‚\nand then go over the schedule… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、夢みたいですよ。まさか私が\n星見プロダクションのマネージャーになれるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still feel like I’m dreaming. I never thought\nI’d ever become a manager at Hoshimi Productions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日とか、ワクワクして夜寝られなくって……\n今だってドキドキしっぱなしなんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so excited last night that I couldn’t sleep.\nAnd even now‚ my heart just won’t stop fluttering!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "面接の時にも、そんなこと言ってたよな\nうちの所属アイドルにもずいぶん詳しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember you saying stuff like that at the interview‚ too.\nYou were also really knowledgeable about our idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃもう、当たり前じゃないですか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ of course I am! How could I not be?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "今どき、星見プロとその所属アイドルを\n知らない人なんて、いませんよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I challenge you to find anyone nowadays who hasn’t heard of\nHoshimi Productions and the idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrskr-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 104.2
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 104.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm007.m4a",
      "text": "川咲さくらちゃん率いる、太陽のように眩しく\n明るさ全開の『サニーピース』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s Sakura Kawasaki’s group‚ dazzling like the sun\nand full of brightness‚ the Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrktn-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm008.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬琴乃ちゃん率いる、月明かりのように\n美麗で繊細な『月のテンペスト』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then there’s Kotono Nagase’s group‚ beautiful and\ndelicate like the moonlight‚ the Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 119.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm009.m4a",
      "text": "数ヶ月前、突如彗星のごとく現れNEXT VENUS\nグランプリを勝ち抜いた超新人グループ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The extraordinary newcomers who appeared out of nowhere\na few months ago‚ and won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm010.m4a",
      "text": "さらに前人未踏のダブル優勝まで成し遂げ\n今や飛ぶ鳥を落とす勢いで引っ張りだこなんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s more‚ they achieved an unprecedented double-win.\nThey are in high demand‚ like everyone wants a piece of them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、二グループとも優勝してから\nテレビ番組やライブへの出演依頼は一気に増えたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true‚ ever since both groups won‚\nwe’ve suddenly received a lot of requests for them to perform on TV and on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm011.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ、それにCDの売れ行きだって好調で\nデイリーチャートにランクインするほどですもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! And their CDs are selling well‚ too.\nSo well‚ in fact‚ that they rank in the daily charts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まあその結果、星見市から通うのが難しくなって\n事務所ごと東京にやって来た訳だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ because of that‚ it’s been challenging to commute from Hoshimi City‚\nso we moved the whole agency over to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm012.m4a",
      "text": "サクセスストーリーですよね～\n星見市で生まれ、絆を深めてきた二グループ十人……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a perfect success story‚ isn’t it?\nTwo groups of ten girls‚ born in Hoshimi City‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm013.m4a",
      "text": "それが今や東京に拠点を移し\nさらなる高みを目指して頑張っている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "strengthened their bonds and moved to Tokyo‚\nto work harder toward reaching even greater heights.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-stm014.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ……尊い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… So precious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（面接の時は、しっかり受け答えの出来る人だと）\n（思ってたんだけど……なんだか変わった子みたいだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（During her interview‚ I was impressed by her straight answers‚）\n（but she seems like a rather strange young lady.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.33333333332,
          "startTime": 180.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n{user}さん、いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚\n{user}-san‚ are you in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、さくら\nちょうど良かった、さっそく顔合わせだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ Sakura.\nPerfect timing. There’s someone I want you to meet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_01-skr002.m4a",
